OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright or
OL,6,Fsunny spells and some showery rain in
OL,7,Fthe evening with occasionally fresh
OL,8,Fsoutheasterly winds. Drier overnight
OL,9,Ffor Orkney with some further outbreaks
OL,10,Fof rain for Shetland.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,13,Ffor Shetland for much of the day, some
OL,14,Fbrighter spells developing later. A
OL,15,Fcloudy morning with some rain for
OL,16,FOrkney, bright spells and showers
OL,17,Flater.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
