OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FBright
OL,6,For sunny spells Tuesday and Wednesday
OL,7,Fwith showers at times, these
OL,8,Foccasionally heavy and thundery. Sunny
OL,9,Fspells and showers Thursday morning,
OL,10,Fcloud and rain spread east later.
